    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aquatints made with a ground obtained by running a normally grounded plate through the press with fine sandpaper placed faced down on it.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
